    <authority>United States: Food and Drug Administration</authority>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine if a combination of three currently approved acne products are safe and
      effective for the treatment of moderate to severe acne
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A Phase IV, Open-Label Study Evaluating the treatment for Combination Acne Therapy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
